import React from 'react'; import '../Confirmation.css'; // Import the global styles function BookingConfirmed({ bookingDetails }) { const { name, email, phone, address, postalCode, serviceName, servicePrice, totalArea, discount, amount, date, timeFrom, timeTo } = bookingDetails; console.log("Received Booking Details in Confirmation:", bookingDetails); // Debugging check return (

Booking Confirmed

Thank you for booking with us, {name}!

{/* User Information */}
Name: {name}
Email: {email}
Phone: {phone}
Address: {address}
Postal Code: {postalCode}
{/* Date and Time */}
Date: {new Date(date).toLocaleDateString()}
Time Slot: {timeFrom} - {timeTo}
{/* Service Information */}
Service Name: {serviceName}
Service Price (per m²): ${servicePrice}
Total Area (sqm): {totalArea} m²
Discount: {discount}%
Total Amount: ${amount}

We look forward to providing you with excellent service!

); } export default BookingConfirmed;
